407
00:24:24,420 --> 00:24:26,272
Come on.

408
00:24:30,300 --> 00:24:33,440
Drink this, and we're still buddies.

409
00:24:34,300 --> 00:24:36,220
This drink settles everything.

410
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:43,260
