but not humiliation. Play again.

630
00:37:12,560 --> 00:37:13,568
Bring it on.

631
00:37:13,568 --> 00:37:15,720
Meng, listen to me.

632
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:19,920
To make your baby smart, start supplementing now.

633
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:24,480
