657
00:38:08,060 --> 00:38:10,640
- I'm not.
- Calm down, calm down.

658
00:38:10,640 --> 00:38:14,260
Honey, check those maternal products
our aunt sent.

659
00:38:14,260 --> 00:38:15,520
Look carefully.

660
00:38:15,520 --> 00:38:17,380
- Got it.
- Already sent.

661
00:38:17,380 --> 00:38:18,880
Already sent.

662
00:38:18,880 --> 00:38:19,980
Look how fast she did it.

663
00:38:19,980 --> 00:38:22,140
Dad, I'll check on Meng.

664
00:38:23,420 --> 00:38:26,420
Alright, stop being mad.

665
00:38:26,420 --> 00:38:28,520
Honey, tired yet?

666
00:38:28,520 --> 00:38:31,420
Not tired. I'm just getting started.

667
00:38:31,420 --> 00:38:32,640
I'll beat them.

668
00:38:32,640 --> 00:38:33,800
I'll help.

669
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:35,300
