- You bring me luck.
- How does this start?

686
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:05,720
Come on.

687
00:39:05,720 --> 00:39:08,608
- You start it.
- Roll the dice now.

688
00:39:08,608 --> 00:39:09,680
You two.

689
