Six! Six!

690
00:39:11,340 --> 00:39:12,380
What's he doing?

691
00:39:12,380 --> 00:39:14,272
Six across.

692
00:39:31,020 --> 00:39:32,920
Take it easy.

693
00:39:32,920 --> 00:39:35,720
No need to be so careful.

694
00:39:39,520 --> 00:39:41,344
Come.

695
00:39:51,980 --> 00:39:54,220
I love days like this.

